      "content": "i get what you're saying about the breathing thing but i'm not a heavy drinker, i just have one glass of wine maybe once a week. it feels like a huge exaggeration to call it a \"real hazard\" for just one drink. if i'm just sitting on my couch at home and not driving or anything, isn't it basically fine to just use it to help me drift off? i just want a definitive answer on whether it's actually dangerous for a light user like me.",
